# 5. 苦しみの底、取った筆の先

Ena: Huff... Huff...
Ena: (Why...?)
Ena: (It's like the more I try to draw, the more confused I get...)
Ena: (At this rate, I'm never gonna be able to prove him wrong... I have to make him acknowledge my talent...)
Ena: (And yet, I haven't been able to draw anything since the exam...)
Ena: (Ugh, my head... I can't go on...)
Ena: (I should lie down and rest for a bit before trying again...)
Ena: Hm? Was that...?
Ena: Maybe it's a notification from PicShare!
Ena: (What if someone liked one of my old illustrations?!)
Ena: (Oh, it's just recommending someone else's post...)
Ena: (I've posted pretty much everything I've drawn, but they've gotten hardly any likes...)
Ena: (I was convinced that was because everyone on PicShare only cared about looking at the manga and the anime art that people post...)
Ena: (But...)
Ena: (Maybe it's because I'm really not that good...)
Ena: (Does no one like my art...?)
Ena: ...!
Ena: Now it's telling me about popular posts! PicShare's been sending me all these pointless notifications since that update...
Ena: (What is this...?)
Ena: (A high school girl got 300 likes just for a selfie...?)
Ena: (Geez, talk about too much editing. She went way overboard under her eyes. Honestly, I'd probably look 100 times cuter.)
Ena: (See? Just hide one eye, touch it up a bit and I'll have 300 likes in no time...)
Ena: Add a hashtag and... Post.
Ena: What am I doing...?
Ena: I'll put it on silent to shut it up...
Ena: Mhm...
Ena: Yikes... I just wanted to rest my eyes, but ended up sleeping for a while...
Ena: What time is it? Where did I put my phone...?
Ena: Huh...? What's with all these notifications...?
Ena: 700 likes...?!
Comments: <Too cute!!> <Super cute!> <Your face is adorable! I wanna see more!>
Ena: Wow, I wasn't expecting this kind of response...
Ena: Oh, another notification... Geez, how viral is this gonna get...?
Ena: No, I shouldn't be acting all satisfied... It's just a stupid selfie...
Ena: Hehe...
Ena: I kinda feel like I can draw something really good now. I'll give it a go after I have breakfast!
Ena: (No...)
Ena: (Nothing's changed... Or have I gotten worse...?)
Ena: (I can't get the image in my head onto paper. It doesn't matter what I draw. The more I try, the worse things get...)
Ena: ...
Ena: I should take a break...
Ena: Hey, I got another notification...!
Ena: (This feels weird... All these people are looking at my selfie...)
Comments: <So cute!> <Do you not have any makeup on?! Your skin's so pretty!>
Ena: ...
Ena: No, this isn't how I want to get noticed...
Ena: Alright, breaktime's over. I'll start over and redraw it from scratch...
Ena: ...
Ena: Why...?
Ena: I don't understand what I'm doing wrong...!
Ena: Ugh... Shut up...!
Comments: <Can you post a makeup video?> <She must be naturally this cute.> <I envy girls with cute faces...>
Ena: ...
Comments: <Post more pics!> <I wanna see more!>
Ena: More pics...?
Ena: (Alright, fine... I'll take one of my upper body. At least I can use it as a reference for drawing human figures.)
Ena: (I'll touch up the colors a bit... Yeah, this should work...)
Ena: ...!
Comments: <Whoa, she's so cute!> <Your eyelashes are so long! Jealous!>
Comments: <Her hair's pretty too.> <And she's so slim.>
Ena: So many comments...
Ena: Am I really that...?
Ena: Yeah, this angle seems like the better choice. As for my light source...
Ena: (I'm getting nowhere with my drawing, so it's okay if I do this for a little bit longer...right?)
Ena: Hey, the one I took last week has 2,000 likes...!
Ena: How awesome am I? That's way more than your run-of-the-mill idol.
Ena: Hehe. Maybe I really am that cute.
Ena: What if this is what I'm really meant to...
Ena: Meant to do...
Ena: Wh-What am I doing...?
Ena: I should be drawing...
Ena: Ugh, no...!!
Ena: This isn't...
Ena: This isn't what I want... I don't want likes for this...
Ena: I have to draw something... Anything!
Ena: But if I lose my ability to draw, then I'd really...
Ena: ...
Ena: Why...?
Ena: Why can't I draw anything...?
Ena: Why am I so bad at this...?!
Ena: (Wh-What time is it...?)
Ena: (I guess it doesn't really matter...)
Ena: (If I really can't draw anymore...)
Ena: (If I can't draw... I might just try to disappear.)
Ena: (I want to go somewhere that's devoid of other people...)
Ena: (If I can just disappear...)
Ena: ...
Ena: (I'm such an idiot... I know full well that this kind of praise is pointless.)
Ena: (And yet, I still want their likes...)
Ena: ...?
Comments: <This song made me cry like a baby. I want to thank everybody who was there for me when I really needed them.>
Ena: (Oh, it's recommending me another post... Wait, it's just someone's opinion on a song.)
Ena: (This has been happening a lot. People write all these comments hoping that other people say that they agree or that they're right...)
Ena: (We all want attention. We just want to be noticed...)
Ena: (That's why we write these sorts of posts, upload pics and try to get likes... To be seen...)
Ena: So stupid...
Ena: (...? Huh? Did I just press play...?)
Ena: Oh...
Ena: (Hang on... This song... It feels really dark, but it's having this weird effect on me...)
Ena: (Who posted this...? K...? Are they famous or something...?)
Ena: Huh...?
Ena: Tears...?
Ena: (My chest... It kinda hurts... Is this...?)
Ena: (Oh, is that it...? I'm in pain...)
Ena: (This song's so sad... It's full of pain and suffering, and makes me really want to disappear...)
Ena: (But...)
Ena: (It's like it's saying, “No, don't disappear yet.”)
Ena: And it's right... I don't want to disappear yet...
Ena: I don't care if I lose my ability to draw... I'll keep drawing...
Ena: (I want to draw...! I want to keep drawing...!)
Ena: (I'm struggling to draw the way I want and don't even know what I want to draw, but...!)
Ena: ...
Ena: Oh...
Ena: (Is that light piercing through the darkness...?)
Ena: (Wait, that gives me an idea...)
Ena: (Like I can't go anywhere right now, but I can see light at the end of the tunnel...)
Ena: (Or like being lost in a really dark forest where only the moon is visible... And it looks so beautiful... But it also makes you want to shout your lungs out...)
Ena: (I don't really know where I'm going with this...!)
Ena: (But I want to use this idea... I want to draw it!!)
Ena: Done...
Ena: I... I actually drew it...
Ena: ... Th-Thank goodness...
Ena: Thank you, K...
Ena: Whoa, my hands are all black... I should wash my hands later.
Ena: However, before I do that...
Ena: (I uploaded it... But still no likes...)
Ena: Tough crowd...
Ena: *Yawn*
Ena: I guess I ended up falling asleep after that... I'm aching all over too. Probably because I drew for so long in such a weird posture...
Ena: That drawing...
Ena: Am I ever gonna be able to draw anything like what I did yesterday again...?
Ena: Oh, a notification...
Ena: (No, I shouldn't look... If I do, I'll get sucked back in.)
Ena: (I know that's gonna happen, but...)
Ena: Hm...? Hold on... That last one wasn't a like...
Ena: A DM...?
Ena: They used my drawing to make a music video...?
Ena: Thank goodness...
Ena: It wasn't a waste after all...
